Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的问题 还是直接去找本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里沉睡着他的遗传基因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且祭品还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不像感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是午饭的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦 昨天就有些不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍术修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊 鸣人的身体不适…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好认真教我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木叶的英雄不过如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 你们听着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要战胜各种困难和挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是体力和运动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但漫无目的地锻炼无益于实战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…经过我的长年修炼 研究出一套方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为 鸣人流强劲动力以及神奇训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来很带劲 哥哥也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握了它 危难时刻你们也能大展身手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢太辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么事 都需要百分百的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先飞奔到河边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说佯攻是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是连这都不懂的笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 我是说被兜利用真是太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以不死之身为荣的你竟会被分尸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不是一样 自爆身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是为了终极艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最崇高的自我献身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少狡辩 还不是挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 训练…结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗 真轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买些饮料来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 真不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…身体不太舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你总是嚷着艺术 艺术的 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽做些造型丑陋的炸弹 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那狗屁仪式才是又臭又长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我还得挺身掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不需要你掩护呢 冒牌的艺术家混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少叫嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了那咒印 你一文不值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就尝尝我的诅咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计你会先被我的艺术给炸飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热身运动已经做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃那边的冰激淋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧看吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都在你们身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然完全没减肥的概念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我伤势痊愈 一定会运动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我严厉地指导你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠夺 掠夺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:12:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去…快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以对哥哥说这么过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被讨厌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…小樱…不用啦…那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么担心你 跟傻瓜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…镇长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之为了尽快通知各位 就匆忙赶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早 这名老者徘徊于镇政厅之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长能平安归来才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛被刺伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我彷徨于荒野之时 总算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多克 真是给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件重要的事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得那晚我给你的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你已经察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是藏于村子祭坛里宝物的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防被偷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将其拆散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给了你及另一名守卫保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜的是 我和他保管的五根都被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅剩的两根 无论如何都要保住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把它交给迪索纳斯严加保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…剩下的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 你好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秽土转生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真机灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很特别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那个胖子 拷问出情报来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半死不活的祭品看来派不上多大用场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠夺 掠夺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去 快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去 快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快从鸣人哥哥的体内出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,像你这样拥有强大力量的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,无论将之用于正道或是邪道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,都必须背负巨大的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,但是你的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,为何想要变强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.51,0:22:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.51,0:23:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,力量 第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,这份执念一定会指引你前进的